## 💼 Business Problem

Healthcare organizations need to monitor key revenue cycle KPIs such as:
- denial rate
- collection rate
- outstanding balances
- department performance

This project simulates how those insights are generated using structured data.

---

## 🧠 Key Insights

- Denial rate is elevated → requires workflow review
- Collection rate below target → follow-up needed
- Oncology and Orthopedics show highest balances

